    {
      "bookmarkId": "605358_1_7800-7880",
      "chapterUid": 1,
      "range": "7800-7880",
      "markText": "那里边的人都是天黑了就睡觉，天亮了就起来工作。一年四季，春暖花开，秋雨，冬雪，也不过是随着季节穿起棉衣来，脱下单衣去的过着。生老病死也都是一声不响的默默的办理。",
      "totalCount": 819,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=605358&chapterUid=1&rangeStart=7800&rangeEnd=7880",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/5f432bd0593cae5f417653c?chapterUid=1&rangeStart=7800&rangeEnd=7880"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "605358_1_9069-9111",
      "chapterUid": 1,
      "range": "9069-9111",
      "markText": "总之，除了这染缸房子在某年某月某日死了一个人外，其余的世界，并没有因此而改动了一点。",
      "totalCount": 806,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=605358&chapterUid=1&rangeStart=9069&rangeEnd=9111",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/5f432bd0593cae5f417653c?chapterUid=1&rangeStart=9069&rangeEnd=9111"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "605358_5_2925-2980",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "2925-2980",
      "markText": "邻居左右因此又都议论起来，说早就该打的，那有那样的团圆媳妇一点也不害羞，坐到那儿坐得笔直，走起路来，走得风快。",
      "totalCount": 735,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=605358&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=2925&rangeEnd=2980",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/5f432bd0593cae5f417653c?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=2925&rangeEnd=2980"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "605358_3_7715-7815",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "7715-7815",
      "markText": "家里边多少年前放的东西，没有动过，他们过的是既不向前，也不回头的生活，是凡过去的，都算是忘记了，未来的他们也不怎样积极的希望着，只是一天一天的平板的，无怨无尤的在他们祖先给他们准备好的口粮之中生活着。",
      "totalCount": 720,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=605358&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=7715&rangeEnd=7815",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/5f432bd0593cae5f417653c?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=7715&rangeEnd=7815"
    },
    {
